'''Underwater Salvageables''' are objects exclusive to ''[[Don't Starve Together]]'', introduced in ''[[Return of Them]]''.

Underwater Salvageables appear when a [[Heavy Item]] sinks into the [[Ocean/DST|Ocean]]. Heavy Items includes [[Chess Pieces]], [[Suspicious Marble]], [[Lunar Altars]], [[Cave-in Boulder]]s, [[Shell Cluster]]s, [[Giant Vegetables]], and [[Sunken Chest]]s.

A [[Pinchin' Winch]] can be used to recover the sunken objects.

=={{pic|32|Placeholder}} Trivia==
* The Underwater Salvageable was introduced in the ''[[Return of Them#She Sells Sea Shells|She Sells Sea Shells]]'' update.
* Any pieces of the three Celestial Altars (Altar, Sanctum or Tribute) that are currently underwater can be pointed out by an [[Astral Detector]].

